    "body": "> @saledjenic I know we have the profile fetching progress implemented in the backend, do you think we need it for this new loading view?\r\n\r\n@alexjba it doesn't have anything to profile fetching and so, was talking about delayed login for recovering account flow. Should be similar to what's discussed above.\r\n\r\nI just wanted to say that the similar/same behaviour is implemented for recovering an account (logic is already developed and may be used in above discussed case as well). At the moment when everything is ready to move to the app, we are displaying the loading animation for 30 seconds just to be sure that the latest backed up messages are received and then move to another state. ",
